🔹 1️⃣ ManagerNotificationRule kya hai?
👉 ManagerNotificationRule = ek SailPoint Rule hai
jo decide karta hai:-
➡️ Manager ko notification bhejna hai ya nahi
➡️ Kaun sa manager / kaun se log notify honge
➡️ Kya message / email jayega

💡 Simple line me:-
👉 “Manager ko kab aur kya notify karna hai” = ManagerNotificationRule

🔹 2️⃣ Ye class hai ya nahi?
👉 ❌ Java class nahi hai
👉 ✅ SailPoint Rule (script/XML based)
Bilkul ApprovalRule ki tarah:-
UI / XML me likhte ho
DB me store hota hai
Runtime pe execute hota hai.

🔹 3️⃣ Ye kab use hota hai?
👉 Jab koi event hota hai:-
Access request submit hua
Approval pending hai
Access granted ho gaya
Access revoke hua
👉 Tab system decide karta hai:-
➡️ Manager ko email bhejna hai ya nahi.

🔹 4️⃣ Iske andar kya hota hai?
✔️ Inputs milte hain:-
identity → user jiska access hai
manager → uska manager
context → SailPointContext
approval / request → optional
✔️ Rule kya karta hai:
Manager identify karta hai
Email bhejne ka decision karta hai
Custom logic apply karta hai